{
  "stem": "27129.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were sending, uh, food, you know, to help, and it was quite a big help.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could smell America already over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was really a great thing, a great job that America is doing the world over for needy people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was the first thing, you know, that I could feel, you know, that-- that somebody is up there, you know, helping.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So, little by little, you know, after [CLEARS THROAT] the war, you know, came closer to an end, you know, we felt a little more free, a little more the burden of war, you know.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then the help that we got from America was also, you know, helped-- helped a lot, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We could have some good clothes, some food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was-- it was quite a great thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, uh, then they came to us, the Russian, uh-- from the KGB, from the militia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they said that we'll be able to go home, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That there's people already started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, and we have to register to-- to go home, and, uh-- it's going to be-- you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because over there, they had already-- it looked like later that we found out that they had already Communist governments in Poland and Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "See, so they didn't mind, you know, if you go home, because it's going to be easier on them to have foreigners in their [? midst. ?] You know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it's going to be better, you know, for Poland that we're going to go back and, you know, they need more people to work, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So one day, you know, it happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We w-- we started going back, but still in cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
